high_descs: Walk straight, turn left at the island, and walk to the counter on your right.
Pick up the lettuce from the counter.
Walk to the fridge to your left.
Place the lettuce in the top section of the fridge.
Turn around, then turn left at the outside of the island and walk around to face it.
Pick up the lettuce from the island.
Walk back to the fridge.
Put the lettuce on the lowest shelf of the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place two heads of lettuce in a fridge.

high_descs: Walk to the right around the table and walk around the table to face the counter to the right of the fridge.
Pick up the head of lettuce on the counter.
Step to the left to face the fridge.
Place the lettuce in the freezer.
Turn around and walk around to face the opposite side of the center table
Pick up the head of lettuce on the table.
Walk to the right around the table and walk around the table and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the head of lettuce in the freezer beside the other head of lettuce.
